snippet.title: Beneath a Dead City - Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Beneath a Dead City is a fantasy colony sim focused on procedurally generating stories and story arcs.

Beneath a Dead City is a semi-sequel to one of my earlier games, Within a Dead City. I expanded on the core gameplay so much that it's switched genres. lol.
